## ğŸ› ï¸ **Troubleshooting**

### **Common Issues**

#### **Application Won't Start**
```bash
# Check if port is available
lsof -i :8090

# Check Docker container logs
docker logs projecthub-frontend

# Rebuild container
docker build -t projecthub-frontend . --no-cache
```

#### **API Connection Issues**
```bash
# Test backend connectivity
curl http://localhost:3009/health

# Check CORS configuration
curl -H "Origin: http://localhost:8090" http://localhost:3009/api/projects
```

#### **Theme Issues**
```bash
# Check localStorage
localStorage.getItem('darkMode')

# Reset theme
localStorage.removeItem('darkMode')
```

> **ğŸ“š Complete troubleshooting guide available in [new-frontend/docs/TROUBLESHOOTING.md](new-frontend/docs/TROUBLESHOOTING.md)**

